long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Arnie Attack is a great shooting platform game. Control soldier in the jungle collect diamonds, kill all enemies for a limited time and finished the level. You need to finished 5 levels to completed this mission. Use arrows keys to move Arnie and space for shoot. Enjoy.
